org.orgName: District Court for the Third Judicial District of Washington Territory

body.p: Office of the Sheriff of King County } ss Washington Territory

I William Cochrane Sheriff of King County W.T. do hereby cerify that I received two writs of Habeas Corpus of which the annexed is a true copy on the 22nd day of November 1888 and personally served the said writs on the 22nd day of November 1888 on J.C. Mitchell Chief of Police and James Bogant Jailor they being the persons named in said writ of Habeas Corpus by delivering one of said writs to each other of said persons, in said King County
Dated at Seattle W.T. Seattle this 22nd day of Nov. 1888 William Cochrane Sheriff of King County W.T. By M. Gadden Deputy
Sheriffs Fees Serving 2 writs $2.00 Copy of Writ .40 Return .50 Travel 2 miles .20 $3.10
